 sight. As he lay flat on his couch, he felt carried sideways by the flow of shadows and, simultaneously, he escorted distant foot-passengers, and visualized now the sidewalk’s surface right under his eyes (with the exhaustive accuracy of a dog’s sight), now the design of bare branches against a sky still retaining some color, or else the alternation of shop windows: a hairdresser’s dummy, hardly surpassing the queen of hearts in anatomic development; a picture framer’s display, with pur